1. host-reconid-import.pl

The host-reconid-import.pl script imports service recon id data from
comma delimited CSV file into corresponding host_invetory tag field in 
Zabbix. 

Usage: host-record-import.pl <options> <filename>
    Where:
        <options>
            --url=<url>             - Zabbix frontend URL
            --username=<username>   - Zabbix user name
            --password=<password>   - Zabbix user password
        <filename> 
	    the name of the file with ReconID data

The CSV file format should be:
,<CI name>,<CI ReconId>,

The script sets the host_inventory tag field to <CI ReconID> for hosts
with host field matching <CI name>

The script is written in perl and requires json and json rpc perl modules.	





